437,"uid":132859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"就好似一個硬幣有兩面<br />\n一個神有三個面"},{"pid":"57830fcabf04883c490615f17684f92ebbe70f3e","tid":833437,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4740935f8ddac828738fb357a1e05ba0a53e993","tid":833437,"uid":69221,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"任佢up<br />\n你啲錢即係我啲錢<br />\n我啲錢唔係你啲錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"咁飛天意麵神有幾多個位格?"},{"pid":"56777e5f04b78d372a03b637cea6b39bf0949089","tid":833437,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"創世紀:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們</span>要照着我們的形象，按着我們的樣式造人<br />\n<br />\n一直以為佢自己同自己講野，原來有三條友自己係到講野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d61473d859152b2b41b0ae0e4834f87de6d93d","tid":833437,"uid":191531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"最接近嘅比喻係水有三個形態（固態液態氣態），但唔同形態終歸都係水<br />\n<br />\n三位一體係講三個位格一個體位，聖父聖子聖神同係天主聖三，而當中：<br />\n<br />\n1. 聖父生聖子<br />\n2. 聖子由聖父所生<br />\n3. 聖神由聖父、聖子共發<br />\n<br />\n聖父聖子聖神各有佢哋特有嘅臨在方式（嚟自下面參考資料）：<br />\n<br />\n(i). 聖父&mdash;創造者<br />\n<br />\n耶穌啟示天主是「父」，不僅因為祂是宇宙和人類的造物主，尤其因為祂在永恆中生了懷中的子，祂的聖言，即「天主光榮的反映，是天主本體的真象」(希1：3) (教理簡編46)<br />\n<br />\n(ii). 聖子&mdash;救贖者<br />\n<br />\n天主子因聖神由童貞瑪利亞取得肉軀，是為了我們人類，並為了我們的得救，這就是說：為使我們罪人與天主和好；為使我們認識天主無限的愛；為作我們聖德的模範；為使我們「成為有分於天主性體的人」(伯後1:4)。(教理簡編85)<br />\n<br />\n(iii). 聖神&mdash;生命的賜與者<br />\n<br />\n聖神被「派遣到我們的心內」(迦4:6)，為使我們獲得天主子女的新生命。(教理簡編136)<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<a href=\"https://dcc.catholic.org.hk/dcc/%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e8%ac%9b%e6%8e%88%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e5%ba%ab/%e6%96%87%e7%8d%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/%e5%a4%a9%e4%b8%bb%e6%95%99%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e7%b0%a1%e7%b7%a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdcc.catholic.org.hk%2Fdcc%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25ac%259b%25e6%258e%2588%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%2596%2599%25e5%25ba%25ab%2F%25e6%2596%2587%25e7%258d%25bb%25e5%258f%258a%25e6%2596%2587%25e4%25bb%25b6%2F%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e6%2595%2599%25e6%2595%2599%25e7%2590%2586%25e7%25b0%25a1%25e7%25b7%25a8&d=AjF55Uvm8a1Lree0xpOGZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9da9f79a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dcc.catholic.org.hk/dcc/%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e8%ac%9b%e6%8e%88%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e5%ba%ab/%e6%96%87%e7%8d%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/%e5%a4%a9%e4%b8%bb%e6%95%99%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e7%b0%a1%e7%b7%a8</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣呢篇英文嘅解得頗詳細：<a href=\"https://www.catholic.com/magazine/online-edition/explaining-the-trinity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.catholic.com%2Fmagazine%2Fonline-edition%2Fexplaining-the-trinity&d=AjF55Uvm8a1Lree0xpOGZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=830f93ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.catholic.com/magazine/online-edition/explaining-the-trinity</a>"},{"pid":"1efb9bc50a9aac8b0481b57abc2204dc2c02e943","tid":833437,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1f950b2b91d95aa8541083f3e8732e3e1d01b38","tid":833437,"uid":130901,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image3.suning.cn/b2c/catentries/000000000131177215_1_800x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage3.suning.cn%2Fb2c%2Fcatentries%2F000000000131177215_1_800x800.jpg&h=c7019203&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"165ba8cd0b0925cbb2caee7c1876f78852965602","tid":833437,"uid":191531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1efb9bc50a9aac8b0481b57abc2204dc2c02e943","tid":833437,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"聖子嘅死係當時人民嘅自由意志加耶穌（有見符合聖父嘅「救世計劃」）而自願而促使嘅，唔係話聖父落聖旨賜死佢，所以唔算自殺（？）"},{"pid":"3ca5b68bd6f90e0e3bb8219a0864c1e1d802ebb5","tid":833437,"uid":104910,"like":0,"disli