olic.com/magazine/online-edition/explaining-the-trinity</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"聖神係自父而發，睇381年尼西亞-君士坦丁信經同埋Canon"},{"pid":"d25fefaccdca720f24bd4d5d47671dfee176f0a4","tid":833437,"uid":50060,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:57:21.000Z","msg":"哦...咁我明點解我細個既時候要三個神父一齊灌輸我聖液了<br />\n<br />\n原來係代表 聖父、聖子、聖神 <br />\n三道聖液係我身體合而為一 變成祝福 終於明白三位神父既好意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a005d916032c265dbe3d9b330158f3697c8ec28b","tid":833437,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T21:47:32.000Z","msg":"non-transitive relation咁解"},{"pid":"5dec8ca7aaec3b7b65f972f4f98da710e1bbd466","tid":833437,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a005d916032c265dbe3d9b330158f3697c8ec28b","tid":833437,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T21:47:32.000Z","msg":"non-transitive relation咁解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:08:24.000Z","msg":"認真講，其實唔一定唔合邏輯 <br />\n<br />\n你只係假定左「是」係 identity  先唔明白 <br />\n位格, personhood 唔一定係 identity <br />\n<br />\n呢度已經唔係神學問題 而係典型嘅哲學問題：<br />\n咩係personhood ，咩係 essence<br />\n有哲學家會話， personhood  係本體嘅心理體現<br />\n如果依呢個講法，的確冇理由話 personhood係 identity<br />\n所以唔一定係 transitive"},{"pid":"53dec68b4a28ad4f7cf2a74b4cc26f58aec428ed","tid":833437,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:34:40.000Z","msg":"打online game 開三個acc"},{"pid":"a81d57fac5786824fc6c83c7e198087acda051b1","tid":833437,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53dec68b4a28ad4f7cf2a74b4cc26f58aec428ed","tid":833437,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:34:40.000Z","msg":"打online game 開三個acc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:38:38.000Z","msg":"係一個acc開三個角色"},{"pid":"004b148d96058ec15ee0f6e577f3e17f5cc98f32","tid":833437,"uid":82710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:48:01.000Z","msg":"口部，西部，屎眼<br />\n三個窿都屬於同一隻臭G都可抽插<br />\n但口不等於西不等於屎眼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌d垃圾中東佬鳩up咁多人信真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b0278f1b85e15763d90ab7f8d19af5fb146f1d","tid":833437,"uid":144466,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T22:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/065551_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F065551_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6d233a18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013b964b6597b176d6aa7e600670ed2075a919d7","tid":833437,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98e69e927fcf52458d2c883a8a5e33aa543d4b8b","tid":833437,"uid":54524,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"你係人，我係人，佢係人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"人地一神論"},{"pid":"8255eb4fc13d491c71ca2084ec819ff6a79f0fab","tid":833437,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d61473d859152b2b41b0ae0e4834f87de6d93d","tid":833437,"uid":191531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"最接近嘅比喻係水有三個形態（固態液態氣態），但唔同形態終歸都係水<br />\n<br />\n三位一體係講三個位格一個體位，聖父聖子聖神同係天主聖三，而當中：<br />\n<br />\n1. 聖父生聖子<br />\n2. 聖子由聖父所生<br />\n3. 聖神由聖父、聖子共發<br />\n<br />\n聖父聖子聖神各有佢哋特有嘅臨在方式（嚟自下面參考資料）：<br />\n<br />\n(i). 聖父&mdash;創造者<br />\n<br />\n耶穌啟示天主是「父」，不僅因為祂是宇宙和人類的造物主，尤其因為祂在永恆中生了懷中的子，祂的聖言，即「天主光榮的反映，是天主本體的真象」(希1：3) (教理簡編46)<br />\n<br />\n(ii). 聖子&mdash;救贖者<br />\n<br />\n天主子因聖神由童貞瑪利亞取得肉軀，是為了我們人類，並為了我們的得救，這就是說：為使我們罪人與天主和好；為使我們認識天主無限的愛；為作我們聖德的模範；為使我們「成為有分於天主性體的人」(伯後1:4)。(教理簡編85)<br />\n<br />\n(iii). 聖神&mdash;生命的賜與者<br />\n<br />\n聖神被「派遣到我們的心內」(迦4:6)，為使我們獲得天主子女的新生命。(教理簡編136)<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<a href=\"https://dcc.catholic.org.hk/dcc/%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e8%ac%9b%e6%8e%88%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e5%ba%ab/%e6%96%87%e7%8d%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/%e5%a4%a9%e4%b8%bb%e6%95%99%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e7%b0%a1%e7%b7%a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdcc.catholic.org.hk%2Fdcc%2F%25e6%2595%2599%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25ac%259b%25e6%258e%2588%25e8%25b3%2587%25e6%2596%2599%25e5%25ba%25ab%2F%25e6%2596%2587%25e7%258d%25bb%25e5%258f%258a%25e6%2596%2587%25e4%25bb%25b6%2F%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e6%2595%2599%25e6%2595%2599%25e7%2590%2586%25e7%25b0%25a1%25e7%25b7%25a8&d=AjF55Uvm8a1Lree0xpOGZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9da9f79a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dcc.catholic.org.hk/dcc/%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e8%ac%9b%e6%8e%88%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e5%ba%ab/%e6%96%87%e7%8d%bb%e5%8f%8a%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6/%e5%a4%a9%e4%b8%bb%e6%95%99%e6%95%99%e7%90%86%e7%b0%a1%e7%b7%a8</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣呢篇英文嘅解得頗詳細：<a href=\"https://www.catholic.com/magazine/online-edition/explaining-the-trinity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.catholic.com%2Fmagazine%2Fonline-edition%2Fexplaining-the-trinity&d=AjF55Uvm8a1Lree0xpOGZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=830f93ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.catholic.com/magazine/online-edition/explaining-the-trinity</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"用水做比喻只會去到形態論呢個異端"},{"pid":"a56db87ad9595286706f9b6005bb3cebbc9439a7","tid":833437,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56777e5f04b78d372a03b637cea6b39bf0949089","tid":833437,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"創世紀:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們</span>要照着我們的形象，按着我們的樣式造人<br />\n<br />\n一直以為佢自己同自己講野，原來有三條友自己係到講野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"其實係可能包括天使"},{"pid":"cade8c2ab14fbfdd0caa3690dea2c6a052faeff5","tid":833437,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"用太陽去做類比可能好啲<br />\n<br />\n聖父= 太陽嘅&quot;本體&quot;<br />\n聖子= 太陽光